WEBVTT

00:14:58.375 --> 00:15:02.809
The entire time that we had been
trying to build it and failing,

00:15:02.833 --> 00:15:06.351
it had evolved by itself
in a flask in the back of the lab.

00:15:06.375 --> 00:15:07.643
(Audience) What?

00:15:07.667 --> 00:15:09.268
(Laughter)

00:15:09.292 --> 00:15:10.643
We finally had a foothold.

00:15:10.667 --> 00:15:13.875
And we used this
to build the first hijacker.

00:15:14.875 --> 00:15:18.667
But we had no evidence
that what we built was a therapy.

00:15:19.792 --> 00:15:24.393
The first hurdle that any therapy
has to clear is testing in a mouse.

00:15:24.417 --> 00:15:26.184
It can be risky.

00:15:26.208 --> 00:15:29.643
In our case, if our mice died,

00:15:29.667 --> 00:15:31.309
so did our funding,